comments: Porter Jr. (DEN) brings his forearm towards Henderson's (POR) front and marginal contact occurs during the drive.
Henderson (POR) cleanly deflects the ball away from Braun (DEN) during the drive.
Murray (POR) and Gordon (DEN) attempt to secure the ball, and the contact during the inbound is marginal.
Henderson (POR) is the last player to touch the ball before the ball goes out of bounds.  Possession is correctly awarded to the Nuggets.
Henderson (POR) is in the paint for less than three seconds when the shot is imminent.
Murray (POR) is moving alongside Gordon's (DEN) path, and the contact during the driving shot attempt is marginal.
Murray (POR) is raising his arm to pursue the rebound, and marginal contact occurs with Gordon (DEN) during his put back attempt.

Replay review of the out of bounds called on Reath (POR) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful. Reath is the last player to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds, and possession is correctly awarded to the Nuggets.
Henderson (POR) is the last player to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds.  Possession is correctly awarded to the Nuggets.
Correctly called 24 second violation.

Henderson (POR) uses his off-arm to deliver contact to Caldwell-Pope's (DEN) face, which affects his ability to defend the driving shot attempt. The crew then triggers a flagrant foul review, and after communicating with the Replay Center, the call stood as a common foul.
Jackson (DEN) and Henderson (POR) briefly engage and disengage during the inbound.
Reath (POR) is returning his left foot to the floor when his foot makes contact with the ball.
Gordon (DEN) is turning away from Camara (POR) with his hand applied to Camara's torso, and the contact during the shot is marginal.
Murray (POR) and Braun (DEN) pursue the loose ball and marginal arm to arm contact occurs during the rebound.
Jackson (DEN) brushes Camara's (POR) left arm and the contact during the shot near the rim is marginal.
Gordon (DEN) is in the lane for less than three seconds when the shot is imminent.
Jackson (DEN) is moving alongside Henderson's (POR) path, and the contact during the driving shot attempt is marginal.
Banton (POR) commits a take foul on Caldwell-Pope (DEN).
Banton (POR) brings his hands towards Jackson's (DEN) side, and the contact during the inbound is marginal.
Banton (POR) commits a take foul on Jackson (DEN).
Braun (DEN) swipes down and makes contact with Henderson's (POR) right arm/elbow that alters his driving shot attempt.
Reath (POR) commits a take foul on Gordon (DEN).
Camara (POR) commits a take foul on Jackson (DEN).
Jackson (DEN) contests the shot attempt and avoids making contact with Murray (POR).
